close_reason: Completed planned scope for Harden chained sandbox env detection per segment and preserved verification context for future changes.
body: Current sandbox env detection in pm test --add is command-wide. Chained commands can pass validation when PM_PATH and PM_GLOBAL_PATH are set in one segment but an unsafe direct runner appears in a different segment. Tighten validation so each chained direct-runner segment must either use node scripts/run-tests.mjs or explicitly set both env vars.
